sub_title: Transformational Mental Coach | Mentor | Trainer | Consultant Elevating Organisations and Individuals
summary:
As an Associate Certified ICF coach and NLP Practitioner and hypnotherapist, I specialize in helping women overcome self-doubt, expand their personal leadership skills and transform into confident, powerful founders and leaders.

In my work with women, I combine scientifically proven techniques from psychology, coaching, and neuroscience, as well as insights from my personal life while leveraging my 20 years of corporate experience to deliver effective coaching and mentoring services. 

I have…

Successfully worked with numerous of women founders and leaders to help them overcome limiting beliefs and achieve their goals.
Developed unique online membership programs providing personalized guidance and support to enable women to realize their full potential as well as 1:1 coaching sessions
Helped clients achieve significant results, e.g. increased revenue, improved productivity, enhanced leadership capabilities, a significant increase of confidence and personal leadership, overall happiness, and greater personal fulfillment.

My mission is to help women founders and leaders to overcome self-doubt, expand personal leadership and transform into confident, powerful founders & leaders so the world can be a place where equality thrives. 

If you would like to find out more, please reach out at hello@chantalehlen.com or book a free consultation following the link on this page.

Corporate Background:

With over 15 years’ of experience in providing comprehensive project and team leadership and support and management services across various sectors to CEOs and company founders, I've developed a reputation as a dynamic, and people-orientated professional, aiding startups to develop into industry players. 

As an Entrepreneurial expert, I possess an array of transferrable skills, that I've been able to apply in various scenarios. 

I've effectively leveraged my interpersonal skills to cultivate cohesive, collaborative initiatives, consolidating directives, refining strategic approaches, and advancing the enterprise toward corporate objectives. 

I have established a track record of successfully motivating both individuals, as well as corporate, growth. 

Over the years I have demonstrated my team coaching expertise, assisting corporations, start-ups, or government projects, with the implementation of best practices, improving engagement and productivity, ultimately achieving long-term performance excellence. 

With that, I welcome our connection!
